file.name: get_with_path_param.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Entities
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /person/{personId}:
    get:
      summary: Find person by ID
      description: Returns a single person
      operationId: getPersonById
      parameters:
        - name: personId
          in: path
          description: ID of person to return
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        "200":
          description: successful operation
